Ayah!

00:21:36.840 --> 00:21:39.680 line:20%
'Sayang.  Savi?'

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:42.960 line:20%
'Savi?  Savi!'

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:45.400 line:20%
'Savi!'

00:21:45.800 --> 00:21:47.280 line:20%
'Virat?
- Kemana dia bisa pergi?'

00:21:48.320 --> 00:21:49.480 line:20%
'Apa masalahnya?'

00:21:49.560 --> 00:21:51.600 line:20%
'Ayah, aku tidak bisa menemukan Savi!
