00:21:51.840 --> 00:21:52.720 line:20%
'Aku tidak tahu di mana dia!'

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:56.720 line:20%
'Mungkinkah Sai membawanya?'

00:22:03.720 --> 00:22:06.960 line:20%
'Jagtap!  Ya!'

00:22:07.520 --> 00:22:09.200 line:20%
'Dia pasti mengambil putriku!'

00:22:12.120 --> 00:22:14.640 line:20%
'Aku tidak akan mengampuni dia!'